# Backup in Znuny

Daliy  backups of SQL DB
## Locations

1. /var/backups/otrs - Local Storage
2. /mnt/znuny - Mount Location
3. \\192.168.147.110/znuny  Shared folder through OneDrive (instead of messing around with rsync and onedrive)

## Code
`#!/bin/bash

# Timestamp
DATE=$(date +%F_%H-%M)

# Backup destination
BACKUP_FILE="/mnt/znuny/znuny_backup_$DATE.sql"

# Run the backup
mysqldump -u root otrs > "$BACKUP_FILE"`
